title: Synaptic Backlash
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

If a [[Tervigon]] is slain, all friendly units of Gaunts within 12" treat the Tervigon as though it were a vehicle that had just exploded as per the ''Explodes!'' result on the Vehicle Damage Table, except that the blast radius is 2d6". All other units are unaffected by the "explosion". Resolve all damage before removing the Tervigon as a casualty.